YOUR INVOLVEMENT CAN
GREATLY ENHANCE

00:01:32.330 --> 00:01:34.930
BABY'S SOCIAL AND
COGNITIVE GROWTH

00:01:34.930 --> 00:01:37.660
FROM THE MOMENT HE COMES
HOME FROM THE HOSPITAL.

