BY THE END OF THE FIRST
MONTH YOUR BABY WILL PROBABLY

00:06:23.530 --> 00:06:26.360
BE ABLE TO LIFT HER HEAD
BRIEFLY WHEN ON HER STOMACH

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:30.430
AND HOLD HER HEAD STEADY FOR A
FEW SECONDS WHEN HELD UPRIGHT

00:06:30.430 --> 00:06:33.000
SHE MAY ALSO BE ABLE TO
FOCUS ON A FACE,

