AND SHE STILL, YOU KNOW,
NEEDS ME FOR EVERYTHING

00:06:54.330 --> 00:06:56.100
BUT WHEN SHE
BEGINS TO COMMUNICATE,

00:06:56.100 --> 00:06:57.600
IT'S A GREAT FEELING.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:01.100
THE SATISFACTION THAT
SHE'S HAPPY AND, YOU KNOW,

00:07:01.100 --> 00:07:04.430
IS LOVED AND
UNDERSTANDS THAT.

