WITHIN A MONTH, AS YOUR
BABY STARTS LAUGHING,

00:07:06.730 --> 00:07:09.530
PLAYING WITH HER HANDS
AND FEET, GRASPING ITEMS

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:12.130
AND BRINGING HER HANDS
TOGETHER FOR PATTY CAKE,

00:07:12.130 --> 00:07:14.930
IT DAWNS ON YOU THAT THIS
LITTLE PERSON DEPENDS ON YOU

00:07:14.930 --> 00:07:18.660
EACH DAY FOR FOOD,
COMFORT, LOVE AND REASSURANCE

00:07:18.660 --> 00:07:25.960
AND YOU
ARE DOING A GREAT JOB!

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:27.760
FOR MOST PARENTS AND
CAREGIVERS,

00:07:27.760 --> 00:07:30.000
COOING IS A WELCOME
STEP UP FROM CRYING

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.930
ON THE COMMUNICATION LADDER.

00:07:31.930 --> 00:07:33.360
AND IT'S JUST
THE BEGINNING.

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:35.660
FROM 1 TO 3 MONTHS OF
AGE, BABY WILL START

00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:37.960
LAUGHING OUT LOUD,
SQUEALING AND EVEN

00:07:37.960 --> 00:07:41.060
ADDING A FEW CONSONANTS
TO HER REPERTOIRE.

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:43.560
WHEN BABIES BEGIN
EXPERIMENTING WITH CONSONANTS

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:46.300
THEY USUALLY DISCOVER
ONE OR TWO AT A TIME

00:07:46.300 --> 00:07:48.460
AND REPEAT THE
SAME COMBINATION.

00:07:48.460 --> 00:07:51.730
GET READY FOR MA-MA, DA-DA,
JU-JU, WA-WA

00:07:51.730 --> 00:07:54.400
AND MANY MORE FUN NAMES.

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.130
NOW IS THE PERFECT TIME
TO HELP ENHANCE

00:07:56.130 --> 00:07:58.300
YOUR BABY'S COMMUNICATION
MILESTONES.

00:07:58.300 --> 00:08:01.460
IT'S A GOOD IDEA TO TALK
TO HER THROUGHOUT THE DAY.

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:05.500
AND FOCUS ON A LOT OF DIRECT
FACE-TO-FACE COMMUNICATION.

