THAT REQUIRE THE BABY TO
GRASP AND REACH FOR ITEMS.

00:08:37.860 --> 00:08:40.500
ENCOURAGING THE DEVELOPMENT
OF ALL THE SENSES -

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:43.900
SIGHT, SOUND, TOUCH,
TASTE AND EVEN SMELL

00:08:43.900 --> 00:09:07.860
WILL CONTRIBUTE
TO BABY'S INTELLECTUAL GROWTH.

