AND I THINK PROBABLY
HIS TALKING.

00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:16.660
HE'S TALKING.

00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.230
HE DOES A LOT OF
THE, YOU KNOW,

00:10:18.230 --> 00:10:22.960
THE BABA'S AND STUFF LIKE
THAT AND IT'S GREAT.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:25.200
PLAYTIME IS MORE
INTERACTIVE NOW AS BABY

