TRANSFER OBJECTS FROM ONE
HAND TO ANOTHER, AND IF

00:11:03.230 --> 00:11:05.360
YOU'RE NOT CAREFUL, YOU
MAY EVEN EXPERIENCE

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:11.360
A LITTLE FOOD ON YOUR FACE,
AND EVERYWHERE ELSE.

