00:11:43.430 --> 00:11:44.660
HE TALKS.

00:11:44.660 --> 00:11:51.000
HE SAYS DA-DA AND GA-GA
AND GOO-GOO WHICH IS,

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:53.460
YOU KNOW, YOU NEVER REALLY
THOUGHT THAT BABIES

